---
// Pricing.astro
---
<section class="section bg-radial-cyan" id="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">💳 Pricing</div>
      <h2>Start with a pilot. Scale with production AI adoption.</h2>
      <p>Pricing scales with governed AI workflows - aligning cost to operational exposure rather than arbitrary seat counts.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing model note -->
    <div class="pricing-model-note">
      <span class="mono">// Value metric: Per Agentic Workflow Governed</span>
      <span>Aligns cost to operational ROI — not arbitrary seat counts</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing cards -->
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <!-- Tier 1 - Recommended -->
      <div class="pricing-card card pricing-card--recommended" id="pricing-pilot">
        <div class="pricing-recommended-badge">
          <span>⭐ Start Here</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-tier-label">Design Partner Pilot</div>
        <h3>Design Partner Pilot</h3>
        <div class="pricing-price">
          <span class="price-amount">$25,000</span>
        </div>
        <div class="price-context">Up to 25 workflows for Pilot</div>

        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            OpenTelemetry ingestion setup
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Forensic Reasoning Replay
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Sample DORA Evidence Pack generation
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Architecture review session
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Staging data only — no SOC-2 required
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="pricing-note">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          Designed to stay within VP discretionary signing authority
        </div>

        <a href="mailto:madan@quirkylabs.ai?subject=Phronesis%20Design%20Partner%20Pilot&body=Hi%20Madan%2C%0A%0AI%27m%20interested%20in%20the%20Phronesis%20Design%20Partner%20Pilot.%0A%0AOrganisation%3A%20%0ARole%3A%20%0AUse%20case%3A%20" class="btn btn-primary pricing-cta" id="pricing-cta-pilot">
          Start Pilot Discussion
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 2 -->
      <div class="pricing-card card" id="pricing-production">
        <div class="pricing-tier-label">Production License</div>
        <h3>Production License</h3>
        <div class="pricing-price">
          <span class="price-amount">$120,000</span>
          <span class="price-period">/ year</span>
        </div>
        <div class="price-context">Production governance for up to 25 workflows</div>

        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Everything in Design Partner Pilot
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Live production telemetry ingestion
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            1-Click DORA Evidence Pack export
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Append-only ledger with hash proofs
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Autonomous Data Mirror (SQL + NDJSON)
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Dedicated Slack support channel
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="pricing-note">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          Operationalize governed AI workflows without building internal forensic infrastructure.
        </div>

        <a href="mailto:madan@quirkylabs.ai?subject=Phronesis%20Production%20License&body=Hi%20Madan%2C%0A%0AI%27m%20interested%20in%20the%20Phronesis%20Production%20License.%0A%0AOrganisation%3A%20%0ARole%3A%20%0AWorkflow%20we%27d%20like%20to%20govern%3A%20" class="btn btn-ghost pricing-cta" id="pricing-cta-production">
          Request Production License
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 3 -->
      <div class="pricing-card card" id="pricing-enterprise">
        <div class="pricing-tier-label">Enterprise Compliance Shield</div>
        <h3>Enterprise Compliance Shield</h3>
        <div class="pricing-price">
          <span class="price-amount">Custom Deployment</span>
        </div>
        <div class="price-context">Organization-wide AI governance coverage</div>

        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Everything in Core License
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Enterprise-scale governed AI workflows
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Centralized Board-Level Risk Dashboard
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Multi-business-line coverage
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Dedicated SLA guarantees (99.9% uptime)
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            Custom on-premise / VPC deployment
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            SR 26-2 Model Risk validation support
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="pricing-note">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          When you govern 25+ agents, we become core infrastructure
        </div>

        <a href="mailto:madan@quirkylabs.ai?subject=Phronesis%20Enterprise%20Shield&body=Hi%20Madan%2C%0A%0AI%27m%20interested%20in%20the%20Phronesis%20Enterprise%20Compliance%20Shield.%0A%0AOrganisation%3A%20%0ARole%3A%20%0AScale%20of%20deployment%20(# of agents)%3A%20" class="btn btn-ghost pricing-cta" id="pricing-cta-enterprise">
          Review Enterprise Governance Requirements
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
/* Model note */
.pricing-model-note {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
}

/* Grid */
.pricing-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.25rem;
  align-items: start;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

/* Card */
.pricing-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}

.pricing-card--recommended {
  border-color: var(--color-cyan);
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.05) 0%, var(--color-surface) 50%);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card), 0 0 60px rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
  transform: scale(1.02);
  overflow: visible !important;
}
.pricing-card--recommended:hover {
  transform: scale(1.02) translateY(-4px);
}

.pricing-recommended-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: -14px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-cyan), var(--color-blue));
  color: var(--color-bg);
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.pricing-tier-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.pricing-card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; }

.pricing-price {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.price-amount {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1;
}
.price-period {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
}
.price-context {
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  margin-top: -0.5rem;
}

.pricing-features {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  flex: 1;
}
.pricing-features li {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
}
.feat-check {
  color: var(--color-green);
  font-weight: 700;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}

.pricing-note {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
  font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.4;
  padding: 0.5rem 0.6rem;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
}

/* ROI comparison */
.pricing-roi {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 0.75rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.15);
}
.roi-label { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.roi-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  padding: 0.25rem 0;
}
.roi-row + .roi-row { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
.roi-cost { color: var(--color-red); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; }
.roi-save { color: var(--color-green); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; }

.pricing-cta { justify-content: center; width: 100%; }

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; margin-inline: auto; }
  .pricing-card--recommended { transform: none; }
  .pricing-card--recommended:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
}
</style>
